    </div>
  </div>


  {# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════
     3. TWO SERVICE CARDS
  ═══════════════════════════════════════════════ #}
  <section
    id="lam-services"
    class="mb-section section-padding"
    aria-labelledby="lam-services-heading"
  >
    <div class="container-custom">
      <header class="mb-header text-center mx-auto mb-10">
        <span class="mb-eyebrow justify-center">Две процедури, един поглед</span>
        <h2 id="lam-services-heading" class="mb-title text-center mt-2">
          Вежди или мигли — или и двете
        </h2>
        <p class="mb-lead text-center mt-3 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Ламинирането е щадяща процедура, която изважда максимума от това, което вече имаш — без изкуственото, без натовареността.
        </p>
      </header>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-6 md:grid-cols-2 max-w-4xl mx-auto">

        {# Eyebrow lamination card #}
        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-[rgba(201,169,138,0.38)] bg-white px-7 py-8 shadow-[0_8px_22px_rgba(44,26,14,0.06)]">
          <div class="mb-5 flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-[#f5ede4]">
            <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-[#c9a98a]" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M4 15s1-1 4-1 5 2 8 2 4-1 4-1V3s-1 1-4 1-5-2-8-2-4 1-4 1z"/><line x1="4" y1="22" x2="4" y2="15"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink mb-3">Ламиниране на вежди</h3>
          <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-[#7a6558] mb-5">
            Оформя, фиксира и подрежда косъмчетата на веждите в желаната посока за по-плътен и изразителен вид. Без нужда от ежедневен гел или молив. При желание се комбинира с боядисване.
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-ink">
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
              <svg class="h-4 w-4 shrink-0 text-[#c9a98a]" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
              Подходящо за непокорни и редки вежди
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
              <svg class="h-4 w-4 shrink-0 text-[#c9a98a]" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
              Резултатът трае 4–6 седмици
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
              <svg class="h-4 w-4 shrink-0 text-[#c9a98a]" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
              Подхранващо действие върху косъма
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
              <svg class="h-4 w-4 shrink-0 text-[#c9a98a]" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
              Може да се комбинира с боядисване
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        {# Lash lamination card #}
        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-[rgba(201,169,138,0.38)] bg-white px-7 py-8 shadow-[0_8px_22px_rgba(44,26,14,0.06)]">
          <div class="mb-5 flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-[#f5ede4]">
            <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-[#c9a98a]" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M2 12s3-7 10-7 10 7 10 7-3 7-10 7-10-7-10-7Z"/><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3"/><path d="M12 5V3M17 7l1.5-1.5M19 12h2M17 17l1.5 1.5M12 19v2M7 17l-1.5 1.5M5 12H3M7 7 5.5 5.5"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink mb-3">Ламиниране на мигли</h3>
          <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-[#7a6558] mb-5">
            Извива, подхранва и визуално удължава естествените мигли без изкуствени косъмчета. По-отворен и изразителен поглед с естествен резултат — без спирала.
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-ink">
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
              <svg class="h-4 w-4 shrink-0 text-[#c9a98a]" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
              Без изкуствени мигли или лепило
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
              <svg class="h-4 w-4 shrink-0 text-[#c9a98a]" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
              Резултатът трае 6–8 седмици
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
              <svg class="h-4 w-4 shrink-0 text-[#c9a98a]" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
              Подхранва в дълбочина
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
              <svg class="h-4 w-4 shrink-0 text-[#c9a98a]" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
              Може да се добави оцветяване
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

      </div>

      <div class="mt-10 text-center">
        <a href="{{ bookingUrl }}" class="btn-primary" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
          Запази час
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>


  {# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════
     4. GALLERY
  ═══════════════════════════════════════════════ #}
  <section
    id="lam-gallery"
    class="mb-section section-padding bg-white/70"
    aria-labelledby="lam-gallery-heading"
  >
    <div class="container-custom">
      <header class="mb-header text-center mx-auto mb-5">
        <span class="mb-eyebrow justify-center">Резултати</span>
        <h2 id="lam-gallery-heading" class="mb-title text-center mt-2">
          Снимките говорят сами
        </h2>
        <p class="mb-lead text-center mt-3">
          Естествен резултат, подчертан поглед — без грим, без натоварване.
        </p>
      </header>
    </div>

    {% if lb.gallery and lb.gallery.length %}
    <div class="mb-bubbles-wrap pt-5" data-lp-lam-bubbles-wrap>
      <div class="container-custom">
        <div class="mb-bubbles-head">
          <p class="mb-bubbles-label" id="lp-lam-gallery-label">Галерия</p>
          <div class="mb-bubbles-nav" aria-hidden="true">
            <button type="button" class="mb-bubbles-arrow mb-bubbles-arrow--prev" data-lp-lam-prev aria-label="Предишна снимка">
              <svg class="mb-arrow-icon" viewBox="0 0 32 32" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.35" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><polyline points="21 8 12 16 21 24" vector-effect="non-scaling-stroke"/></svg>
            </button>
            <button type="button" class="mb-bubbles-arrow mb-bubbles-arrow--next" data-lp-lam-next aria-label="Следваща снимка">
              <svg class="mb-arrow-icon" viewBox="0 0 32 32" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.35" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><polyline points="11 8 20 16 11 24" vector-effect="non-scaling-stroke"/></svg>
            </button>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mb-bubbles" role="list" data-lp-lam-bubbles aria-labelledby="lp-lam-gallery-label">
        {% for item in lb.gallery %}
        <figure
          class="mb-bubble{% if item.src | isVideoPath %} mb-bubble--video{% endif %}"
          role="listitem"
          data-lp-lam-gallery-trigger
          data-lp-lam-gallery-index="{{ loop.index0 }}"
        >
          {% if item.src | isVideoPath %}
          <video
            src="{{ item.src | url }}"
            data-lp-lam-gallery-item
            data-lp-lam-gallery-index="{{ loop.index0 }}"
            muted playsinline loop preload="metadata"
            aria-label="{{ item.alt | default('Ламиниране — видео') }}"
          ></video>
          <span class="mb-bubble__video-badge" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 56 56" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
              <circle cx="28" cy="28" r="26" fill="rgba(255,255,255,0.92)" stroke="rgba(44,26,14,0.1)" stroke-width="1"/>
              <path fill="#3a2415" d="M23 17v22l18-11-18-11Z"/>
            </svg>
          </span>
          {% else %}
          <img
            src="{{ item.src | url }}"
            alt="{{ item.alt | default('Ламиниране — снимка') }}"
            data-lp-lam-gallery-item
            data-lp-lam-gallery-index="{{ loop.index0 }}"
            loading="lazy"
            decoding="async"
          />
          {% endif %}
        </figure>
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
    </div>

    {# Gallery lightbox modal #}
    <div
      id="lp-lam-gallery-modal"
      class="mb-gallery-modal"
      role="dialog"
      aria-modal="true"
      aria-hidden="true"
      aria-label="Галерия ламиниране"
      hidden
    >
      <div class="mb-gallery-modal__backdrop" data-lp-lam-gallery-close></div>
      <div class="mb-gallery-modal__panel" role="document">
        <button type="button" class="mb-gallery-modal__close" data-lp-lam-gallery-close aria-label="Затвори галерията">&times;</button>
        <button type="button" class="mb-gallery-modal__arrow mb-gallery-modal__arrow--prev" data-lp-lam-gallery-prev aria-label="Предишна снимка">
          <svg class="mb-arrow-icon" viewBox="0 0 32 32" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.35" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><polyline points="21 8 12 16 21 24" vector-effect="non-scaling-stroke"/></svg>
        </button>
        <div class="mb-gallery-modal__stage" data-lp-lam-gallery-stage>
          <div class="mb-gallery-modal__clip">
            <img class="mb-gallery-modal__image" data-lp-lam-gallery-image src="" alt="" />
            <video class="mb-gallery-modal__image" data-lp-lam-gallery-video playsinline controls hidden></video>
          </div>
        </div>
        <button type="button" class="mb-gallery-modal__arrow mb-gallery-modal__arrow--next" data-lp-lam-gallery-next aria-label="Следваща снимка">
          <svg class="mb-arrow-icon" viewBox="0 0 32 32" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.35" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><polyline points="11 8 20 16 11 24" vector-effect="non-scaling-stroke"/></svg>
        </button>
      </div>
    </div>
    {% endif %}

  </section>


  {# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════
     5. PAIN POINTS
  ═══════════════════════════════════════════════ #}
  <section
    class="mb-section section-padding"
    aria-labelledby="lam-pain-heading"
  >
    <div class="container-custom">
      <header class="mb-header text-center mx-auto mb-10">
        <span class="mb-eyebrow justify-center">Подходящо ли е за теб?</span>
        <h2 id="lam-pain-heading" class="mb-title text-center mt-2">
          Разпознаваш ли се?
        </h2>
      </header>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-5 sm:grid-cols-3 max-w-4xl mx-auto">

        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-[rgba(201,169,138,0.38)] bg-white px-6 py-7 shadow-[0_8px_22px_rgba(44,26,14,0.06)] text-center">
          <div class="mx-auto mb-4 flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-[#f5ede4]">
            <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-[#c9a98a]" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><polyline points="12 6 12 12 16 14"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-ink mb-2">Сутринта е rush — грим или природа?</h3>
          <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-[#7a6558]">Нанасяш спирала, оправяш вежди с гел — и вече си закъсняла. Дори в почивен ден.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-[rgba(201,169,138,0.38)] bg-white px-6 py-7 shadow-[0_8px_22px_rgba(44,26,14,0.06)] text-center">
          <div class="mx-auto mb-4 flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-[#f5ede4]">
            <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-[#c9a98a]" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M2 12s3-7 10-7 10 7 10 7-3 7-10 7-10-7-10-7Z"/><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-ink mb-2">Веждите или миглите изглеждат плоски</h3>
          <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-[#7a6558]">Редки, прави или непокорни косъмчета, от които погледът ти изглежда умален и неизразителен.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-[rgba(201,169,138,0.38)] bg-white px-6 py-7 shadow-[0_8px_22px_rgba(44,26,14,0.06)] text-center">
          <div class="mx-auto mb-4 flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-[#f5ede4]">
            <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-[#c9a98a]" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M20.84 4.61a5.5 5.5 0 0 0-7.78 0L12 5.67l-1.06-1.06a5.5 5.5 0 0 0-7.78 7.78l1.06 1.06L12 21.23l7.78-7.78 1.06-1.06a5.5 5.5 0 0 0 0-7.78z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-ink mb-2">Искаш естествено, не изкуствено</h3>
          <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-[#7a6558]">Уморила си се от тежките екстеншъни или натрапчивия грим. Искаш да изглеждаш добре и без нищо по лицето.</p>
        </div>

      </div>

      <div class="mx-auto mt-12 max-w-2xl text-center">
        <p class="mb-lead">
          Ламинирането е отговорът: процедура с <em>щадящи продукти</em>, без изкуствено, без болка — и с резултат, за който хората ще питат какво е различното по теб, без да могат да го посочат.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-7">
          <a href="{{ bookingUrl }}" class="btn-primary" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
            Запази час сега
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>


